file_content.text: Corellia in flames... But it could have been so much worse.
We finish the Empire on Corellia, or it's over, for all of us.
So on top of everything else, now we have a rescue to plan.
Best of luck capturing the Javelin, Jedi. I... I mean it.
Voss might make a nice resort world. Once we kick out the Empire.
All those things I said to Grell. I can never take them back.
Why are you standing here when Grell needs you? Go!
So, we're recruiting ancient alien prisoners. Well, the Empire will never see it coming.
Those masters of yours had better come up with something good.
I called Blaesus so many names, and all this time, he was...
You think Blaesus is a traitor? Have you met him?
Once those pirates are gone, Hoth might actually be a smart investment.
I'm sorry we didn't tell you about Attis Station, Jedi. I assure you it won't happen again.
I hope you and "Zenith" enjoy playing politics. The rest of us have work to do.
Rather young to be a Jedi Master, aren't you?
Later, Jedi, I have an urgent call on standby.
